        OS version that is newer than our current OS version. [CHAR LIMIT=100] -->
    <string name="install_failed_older_sdk" translatable="false">The package only works on newer versions.</string>
    <!-- Reason displayed when installation fails because the package could not be verified
        because the package verifier rejected it. [CHAR LIMIT=100] -->
    <string name="install_failed_verify_failed" translatable="false">The package did not pass verification and cannot
        be installed.</string>
